1.  Introduction

The goal of this theme is to integrate the IceWM environment with the 'Simple' GTK theme and 'gnome' icon theme. An alternative menu button has been provided for users of Ubuntu Linux.


2.  Installation

This directory ("IceSimple") should be copied to your IceWM theme directory, usually /usr/share/icewm/themes.


3.  Contact info / links

You can obtain the latest IceWM source from

	http://sourceforge.net/projects/icewm

and the latest version of this theme from

	http://freshmeat.net/projects/icesimple

Any queries/suggestions mail to thomas@trueFormat.co.uk


